HRMbuild Truck Transport company has successful experience in road freight transport market since 1995. Our 20 years' internal and international truck transport experience is at your service. We know this market very well, we know its advantages, and we also know 'pitfalls' of road transport. Turning to us, customer always receives the required number of proposals on the transport of its cargo from different carriers, and each time selects only the most profitable. All carriers of HRMbuild (companies professionally engaged in cargo transportation) undergo compulsory registration procedure, providing us with state documents in their line of business, for example, a license for international road transport, or a license for internal freight transportation.
